<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>Animation</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="styles.css">
</head>
<body>
  <div class="box"></div>

  <script src="script.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
```

CSS (styles.css):
```css
.box {
  width: 100px;
  height: 100px;
  background-color: red;
  position: relative;
  animation-name: move;
  animation-duration: 2s;
  animation-iteration-count: infinite;
}

@keyframes move {
  0% {
    left: 0;
  }
  50% {
    left: 200px;
    background-color: blue;
  }
  100% {
    left: 0;
  }
}
